data.title: Base 2 Space
data.meta_description:
I am participating in Seattle’s Most Iconic Climb, Base 2 Space on September 29th, to support Fred Hutch through the Space Needle Foundation. Donate today and help us get closer to our $1,000,0000 goal!
The Space Needle Foundation is proud to support Fred Hutchinson Cancer Center, a world-renowned organization dedicated to preventing and eliminating cancer and infectious disease. All donations raised during Base 2 Space will be directed to Fred Hutch and the Space Needle Foundation. As a component of the Seattle Foundation, the Space Needle Foundation is committed to elevating our collective future by supporting organizations who are at the forefront of transforming lives and make a positive difference in the Puget Sound region and beyond.
